---
title: Mediterranean Roasted Eggplant & Chorizo Trottole with Cherry Tomatoes & Crumbly Cheese
description: Add layers of flavour to trottole with an array of rainbow veggies roasted in Mediterranean-inspired seasonings. Paired with a rich
cherry tomato sauce, chorizo and aromatic thyme, your finished dish will be transformed into a taste sensation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-fusilli-roasted-eggplant-1cf35319.jpg
